<head>
<title>Help: Setting up manager notification options</title>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=iso-8859-1">
<link href="../style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
</head>

<body>
<p class="titlebold">Setting up manager notification options</p>
<p class="text">To change the notification options, go to Browse under Users
  in the main VariaPrint&#8482; manager menu and select the &quot;Manager accounts&quot; submenu.
  Select &quot;Notification options...&quot; for your account and &quot;Access
  / Notification options ...&quot; for other managers to change the notification
options. </p>
<p class="text">See also<br>
  <a href="users-approval.php" target="mainFrame">Setting
up approval managers</a><br>
<a href="users-vendor.php" target="mainFrame">Setting up vendor managers</a><br>
<a href="users-poapproval.php" target="mainFrame">Setting up managers to approve
PO accounts</a></p>
</body>
</html>
